response.original_title: Daffy Duck And Friends Yankee Doodle Daffy
response.overview: YANKEE DOODLE DAFFY It's the looniest toon of them all in this tale of music & mayhem. DAFFY THE HENPECKED DUCK Daffy finds himself in divorce court after making his son disappear and is at the mercy of the judge, Porky Pig. WABBIT WHO CAME TO SUPPER Elmer inherits $3 million bucks under one condition. Be good to wabbits. FIFTH COLUMN MOUSE The mice put on their bottle cap helmets and battle that double-crossing cat.
response.title: Daffy Duck And Friends Yankee Doodle Daffy
